casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Peter Ugochukwu EMOKAH, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158643
COA: 344667 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion to dismiss the application for leave to appeal is considered, and it is GRANTED. The application for leave to appeal is DISMISSED with prejudice.
